      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOST YOUR MARKER (7) scored by 1.75 lengths last time (19.27) in a Restricted WIN over 350m at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. SURGING SPARK (2) is mixing form and out of the placings last time but was a Grade 4/5 winner three starts ago and moves to Box 2 this time where he has performed well. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Well placed here and can atone this time. WARREGO RAIN (1) hit the ground running from a squeeze draw and was prominent throughout but faded out of it when 7th at Q Lakeside in a Restricted WIN. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. One of the better hopes. CALM AND CRUISY (8) is always hard to beat when she races at this trip.",
